            <p> <span>1 Year</span> Warranty on Defects</p>
          </div>
          <div class="shipping_info_para">
            <p>All our products come with a Limited 1 Year Warranty on defects.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="shipping_img_box">
        <div class="shipping_section_img">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0568/1007/8283/files/Rectangle_61.png?v=1718718996" alt="">
